{"tid":2220324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點擊與工程巴進行激情對話","createTime":"2020-09-27T14:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T17:38:05.000Z","uid":378468,"like":96,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"f5a322a39dc4b5634e761e6905f0e7392ce12d11","tid":2220324,"uid":378468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"荔枝角還押所紙本連登上線了！！<br />\n上連登？唔一定要用電話嘅<br />\n<br />\n尤其而家身陷囹圄嘅手足...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我哋決定發起第一屆嘅荔枝角還押所紙本連登計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位連登仔喺呢個post隨便留言鳩噏<br />\n乜鳩都問下<br />\n<br />\n我哋會print曬出嚟 然後直接比而家喺荔枝角嘅實用工程巴<br />\n<br />\n工程巴由5月30開始已還押4個月<br />\n希望大家同佢打打氣<br />\n<br />\n工程巴會紙本回覆大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後post返上嚟<br />\n同大家瘋狂鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4649cdefee1a57c0ecd1beb20a6537e3a54ad5e4","tid":2220324,"uid":378468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"工程巴真係聖人...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2075675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2075675</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b3520a59f17c508a092e6dba7ac4d575944c23ad","tid":2220324,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\