gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然有一牆之隔 但我永遠與你同在<br />\n你嘅名已經深深烙印喺我心中<br />\n<br />\n為你送上一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n〈奇跡〉，曲／詞／編／監／唱：周博賢<br />\n像巨獸與小子的比拼<br />\n這一役　怎取勝<br />\n<br />\n大石放滿一邊的天秤<br />\n均等值　哪會算清<br />\n<br />\n因此你我縱怨聲過盛<br />\n無一位肯傾聽<br />\n今天靠你踏步伴著我<br />\n到揮手區開創<br />\n<br />\n*奇跡　撼碎牆壁<br />\n潛意識　抗拒去認命<br />\n要跳進醬缸洗去殘跡<br />\n給我奇跡<br />\n憑你的　鬥志去決定<br />\n<br />\n但願個個亦活得率性<br />\n家家亦可爭鳴<br />\n<br />\n毋須起跑線已經比拼<br />\n奔向夢境<br />\n會有讚嘆聲<br />\n<br />\n可惜你我確信的價值<br />\n無一位肯傾聽<br />\n今天靠你踏步伴著我<br />\n到揮手區開創<br />\n<br />\n重複*<br />\n<br />\n相信奇跡　撼碎牆壁<br />\n潛意識　抗拒去認命<br />\n這世界太灰需要顏色<br />\n給我奇跡<br />\n憑你的　鬥志去決定"},{"pid":"6be165de0435e2f1c1bb88d85ebd3f48d2f4eb51","tid":2220324,"uid":117636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T16:01:39.000Z","msg":"巴打，頂撚住呀<br />\n頂住先有希望，好希望你可以出返黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de61a8fb6daae6cbfbb7cd37608cf634a25578b","tid":2220324,"uid":215987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T16:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dbab7fded776cd8fcd10747449310bbb03b2a6","tid":2220324,"uid":1330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:37:50.000Z","msg":"天氣就嚟轉冷<br />\n<br />\n小心身體呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff0acc5e52813c23ae1ad4947db8a4a63d10845","tid":2220324,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"工程巴頂住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望你繼續同女友sweet sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51732b9907c87af770115b1ab8eac5fd41cc1274","tid":2220324,"uid":174812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T22:43:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76808eef4c0fc4a6a5eaf3516c6e2db7b583bc3d","tid":2220324,"uid":263380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d46417a8a996c232d88be3e706e12fd1094d68d","tid":2220324,"uid":314390,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:20:54.000Z","msg":"各位手足希望你們一切安好，本人會每月捐至少1000入612及支援你們家人生活的資金。雖然不管在內還是在外都十分黑暗，但我們堅信黎明終有來到的一天。現在國際已經計畫圍中滅共，相信我們，特別是你們的付出是有收穫的。<br />\n沒有從天而降的英雄，只有挺身而出的凡人<br />\n再次感謝你們對香港的付出<br />\n錚錚鐵骨，不屈如筆"},{"pid":"b83c16f850704ce2ea78cf10eb1b7e92393c38cb","tid":2220324,"uid":208974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96e96a5d2eef5de5a61023c4e9cc8dbb94e2379e","tid":2220324,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df464409c86d8c21811f1f4a64930e97d15a9845","tid":2220324,"uid":291457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:32:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f93abd676e3b86c4d5a25fcf72d73124d0d45531","tid":2220324,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"推 仲快啲上FCC 個Twitter捍衛新聞自由 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2215241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2215241</a>"},{"pid":"6a665015214848d7b9a30a36b33899767b53dcfb","tid":2220324,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"工程巴依家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ea29233e00c5dc9fb98b5405e06b7e47694a84","tid":2220324,"uid":281422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:39:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d6273a127c05e4c5a8b4bb36bdecfc3e49e6c716","tid":2220324,"uid":281422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6be2fad5442433f464af31d699bdc0e0312dd6af